sql:
SELECT category_name
FROM employment_categories
WHERE category_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- Frequent visitors are users who have accessed the data multiple times; 
- Part-time employment statistics are presumed to be of interest to users who have accessed the 'Part-Time Employment' category; 
- The most recent year refers to the year with the highest `year_name` value in the `years` table.

sql:
SELECT region_name
FROM regions
WHERE region_id = (SELECT region_id FROM regions WHERE region_name = 'Texas');

SELECT line_title
FROM employment_lines
WHERE category_id = 1;

SELECT fips, line_title
FROM employment_data
WHERE last_updated = (
    SELECT MAX(upload_date) 
    FROM data_uploads
);
